---
import type { DailyBriefing } from "../types";
interface Props { briefing: DailyBriefing; }
const { briefing } = Astro.props;
---

<section class="signal-filter" aria-labelledby="filter-title">
  <div class="signal-filter__heading">
    <p>今日信号经过四道过滤</p>
    <h2 id="filter-title">扫描了 {briefing.stats.fetched} 个信号，最终保留 {briefing.stats.selected} 条。</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="signal-filter__marquee" aria-hidden="true">
    <div>
      <span>扫描 {briefing.stats.fetched} 条</span><i></i>
      <span>去重后 {briefing.stats.deduplicated} 条</span><i></i>
      <span>LLM 初筛 18 条</span><i></i>
      <span>最终收录 {briefing.stats.selected} 条</span><i></i>
      <span>扫描 {briefing.stats.fetched} 条</span><i></i>
      <span>去重后 {briefing.stats.deduplicated} 条</span><i></i>
      <span>LLM 初筛 18 条</span><i></i>
      <span>最终收录 {briefing.stats.selected} 条</span><i></i>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="signal-filter__steps">
    <div><span>01</span><strong>{briefing.stats.fetched}</strong><p>原始扫描</p></div>
    <div><span>02</span><strong>{briefing.stats.deduplicated}</strong><p>语义去重</p></div>
    <div><span>03</span><strong>18</strong><p>模型初筛</p></div>
    <div><span>04</span><strong>{briefing.stats.selected}</strong><p>总编收录</p></div>
  </div>
  <p class="signal-filter__rejection"><span>过滤样本</span> 只有发布宣传，没有新增工程信息。</p>
</section>
